Jenelle York of York and Spoon provides a
unique take on a thanksgiving staple with

00:03:38.540 --> 00:03:40.200
her citrus spiked cranberry sauce.

00:03:40.200 --> 00:03:45.389
Jenelle: This is a very simple recipe. Now
if you're used to the cranberry sauce in the

00:03:45.389 --> 00:03:50.560
can, this isn't going to be anywhere near
as sweet as you're used to- this is so much

00:03:50.560 --> 00:03:51.319
better for us.

